hitchtroughcombo.name: Hitch & Trough

lantern.description: A Lantern. Place it where you need light, requires low grade fuel to work.

medieval.box.wooden.large.description: Keep your things in this medieval themed wooden storage box. Stores up to 48 items.

wall.frame.lunar2025_a.description: A Lunar New Year themed decorative wall divider with geometric inlay

wall.frame.lunar2025_c.description: A Lunar New Year themed decorative wall divider with floral inlay

small.oil.refinery.name: Small Oil Refinery
small.oil.refinery.description: A small refinery which can produce Low Grade Fuel from Crude Oil.

planter.large.name: Large Planter Box
planter.large.description: A large planter with enough room to plant 9 seeds.

planter.small.name: Small Planter Box
planter.small.description: A small planter with enough room to plant 3 seeds.

planter.triangle.name: Triangle Planter Box
planter.triangle.description: A triangle planter with enough room to plant 4 seeds.

electric.audioalarm.name: Audio Alarm
electric.audioalarm.description: A speaker which will emit a loud warning alarm when powered

smart.alarm.name: Smart Alarm
smart.alarm.description: Sends a notifications to your phone when powered on.

storage.monitor.name: Storage Monitor
storage.monitor.description: The Storage Monitor attaches to the Tool Cupboard and Large Storage Box to monitor the container contents. Output sends a pulse when the container is updated.

electric.battery.rechargable.large.name: Large Rechargeable Battery
electric.battery.rechargable.large.description: A Large Rechargeable Battery. Must have a minimum charge of 5 seconds to discharge. Can be wired in series. Charging rate is dependant on power in, with a maximum of 80% efficiency.

electric.battery.rechargable.medium.name: Medium Rechargeable Battery
electric.battery.rechargable.medium.description: A Medium Rechargable Battery. Must have a minimum charge of 5 seconds to discharge. Can be wired in series. Charging rate is dependant on power in, with a maximum of 80% efficiency.

electric.battery.rechargable.small.name: Small Rechargeable Battery
electric.battery.rechargable.small.description: A small rechargable battery. Must have a minimum charge of 5 seconds to discharge. Can be wired in series. Charging rate is dependant on power in, with a maximum of 80% efficiency.

electric.counter.name: Counter
electric.counter.description: A basic cathode ray tube screen combined with an incremental counter. Can display power received, or can count upwards and allow passthrough when a target is reached.

electric.hbhfsensor.name: HBHF Sensor
electric.hbhfsensor.description: A Heartbeat, Breathing, Humidity and Footstep sensor. Passthrough is equal to the number of humans detected in a 10m radius

electric.laserdetector.name: Laser Detector
electric.laserdetector.description: A gate which allows power to flow while a player is in the beam

electric.pressurepad.name: Pressure Pad
electric.pressurepad.description: A gate which allows power to flow while a player is standing on it

tincan.alarm.name: Tin Can Alarm
tincan.alarm.description: A primitive perimeter alarm made from hanging tin cans. Clatters loudly when disturbed, alerting you to any trespassers. Simple but effective.

electric.digitalclock.name: Digital Clock
electric.digitalclock.description: A digital clock that displays the server time and lets you set alarms to pass power through when ringing. Ideal for synchronizing traps or timed events.

electric.doorcontroller.name: Door Controller
electric.doorcontroller.description: A Door Controller. Will manipulate the state of the closest door when it receives power

electric.furnace.name: Electric Furnace
electric.furnace.description: An electrical version of a furnace that uses electricity instead of a fuel source.

electric.heater.name: Electric Heater
electric.heater.description: Provides warmth in a radius when on

fluid.combiner.name: Fluid Combiner
fluid.combiner.description: Combines three separate fluid connections into one connection.

fluid.splitter.name: Fluid Splitter
fluid.splitter.description: Splits a fluid connection into three separate connections.

fluid.switch.name: Fluid Switch & Pump
fluid.switch.description: A simple switch that enables fluid to pass through. Can be switched on/off manually or via electricity. Can also pump water upwards to higher entities when powered.

electric.andswitch.name: AND Switch
electric.andswitch.description: A logic gate that allows electrical passthrough if BOTH inputs receives power, passthrough amount is the greater of either power source

electric.blocker.name: Blocker
electric.blocker.description: This object prevents passthrough while power is received through its second input.

electrical.branch.name: Electrical Branch
electrical.branch.description: This object allows you to branch power off from a main line by a set amount.

electrical.combiner.name: Root Combiner
electrical.combiner.description: This object combines two root electrical sources into a single signal. Helpful for stringing together low energy batteries or solar panels to produce higher power output. Can be wired in series, can not be used with any non energy producing electrical components.

electrical.memorycell.name: Memory Cell
electrical.memorycell.description: A 1 bit storage component. SET input will set the value to 1 CLEAR input sets the value to 0. Output will provide connected power if value is 1, Inverted output will provide connected power if value is 0. This is also known as a D-Type Flip Flop

electric.orswitch.name: OR Switch
electric.orswitch.description: A logic gate that allows electrical passthrough if EITHER input receives power, passthrough amount is the greater of either power source

electric.random.switch.name: RAND Switch
electric.random.switch.description: This switch will allow passthrough based on a random number. Each time the SET input receives power it will roll true or false to allow passthrough

electric.xorswitch.name: XOR Switch
electric.xorswitch.description: An exclusive-or logic gate that allows electrical passthrough if ONLY ONE input receives power, passthrough amount is whichever single input is active. If BOTH inputs recieve power, passthrough will be zero.

electric.fuelgenerator.small.name: Small Generator
electric.fuelgenerator.small.description: A small electric generator powered by Low Grade Fuel that outputs 40 power.

electric.generator.small.name: Test Generator
electric.generator.small.description: A Mailbox that accepts notes. Only you can access the mail due to a one way slit.

electric.solarpanel.large.name: Large Solar Panel
electric.solarpanel.large.description: A solar panel which converts sunlight into energy. The amount of energy generated is dependent on the sun's intensity and angle to the panel.

electric.igniter.name: Igniter
electric.igniter.description: Ignites nearby objects such as furnaces and campfires when power is received

storageadaptor.name: Storage Adaptor
storageadaptor.description: Attach to a storage container to allow industrial input/output connections.

industrial.combiner.name: Industrial Combiner
industrial.combiner.description: Combines three separate industrial connections into one connection.

industrial.conveyor.name: Industrial Conveyor
industrial.conveyor.description: Moves an item from one container to another.

industrial.crafter.name: Industrial Crafter
industrial.crafter.description: Attaches to a workbench to allow automated crafting.

industrial.splitter.name: Industrial Splitter
industrial.splitter.description: Splits an industrial connection into three separate connections.

powered.water.purifier.name: Powered Water Purifier
powered.water.purifier.description: A device that converts salt water to fresh water while powered.

electric.seismicsensor.name: Seismic Sensor
electric.seismicsensor.description: A small device that detects vibrations within a set range. Will output a different power value depending on the explosive type detected, ideal to know when your time has come.

electric.splitter.name: Splitter
electric.splitter.description: Splits an electrical signal into 3 multiple signals. the amount passed through is equal to the input amount divided by the number of used output slots.

electric.sprinkler.name: Sprinkler
electric.sprinkler.description: A small sprinkler that sprays water around it. Requires a hose connection to supply it with water.

electric.teslacoil.name: Tesla Coil
electric.teslacoil.description: An electrical trap that zaps nearby players when powered. More power supplied will result in higher damage. Loses durability with use.

electric.timer.name: Timer
electric.timer.description: A Timer switch, will pass power through for duration.

electric.cabletunnel.name: Cable Tunnel
electric.cabletunnel.description: Allows you to pass a cable through a wall. Each input will forward the amount it receives to the corresponding output on the other side.

waterpump.name: Water Pump
waterpump.description: Can be placed in a water source to collect that water while powered. Can be connected to other Water entities.

ptz.cctv.camera.name: PTZ CCTV Camera
ptz.cctv.camera.description: A CCTV Camera system can be used for realtime surveillance and security when paired with the Computer Station. This camera has pan, tilt, and zoom capability.

mining.quarry.name: Mining Quarry
mining.quarry.description: Extracts minerals from the ground. Use a Survey Charge to determine the amount of minerals available for extraction in any given area.

target.reactive.name: Reactive Target
target.reactive.description: A reactive target that knocks down when hit, can be reset.

box.repair.bench.name: Repair Bench
box.repair.bench.description: You can repair your items here for a fraction of their construction cost. You may also use this to apply new skins to existing items.

research.table.name: Research Table
research.table.description: You can use this table to learn how to permanently craft items you have found in exchange for scrap.

rug.bear.name: Rug Bear Skin
rug.bear.description: A decorative rug that can be placed on walls, floors, and ceilings. Provides comfort when in close proximity.

rug.name: Rug
rug.description: A decorative rug that can be placed on walls, floors, and ceilings. Provides comfort when in close proximity.

sculpture.ice.name: Ice Sculpture
sculpture.ice.description: An block of ice you can sculpt.

searchlight.name: Search Light
searchlight.description: A Large, wide beam, aimable light source.

secretlabchair.name: Secretlab Chair
secretlabchair.description: A luxurious, comfortable chair for long sessions of CCTV watching.

sign.hanging.banner.large.name: Large Banner Hanging

sign.hanging.description: A double sided hanging sign, to attach to buildings.

sign.hanging.ornate.name: Two Sided Ornate Hanging Sign
sign.hanging.ornate.description: A double sided hanging sign, to attach to buildings.

sign.pictureframe.portrait.description: A portrait oriented canvas for artists paintings.

sign.pictureframe.xl.description: An extra large canvas for artists paintings.

sign.pictureframe.xxl.description: A double extra large canvas for artists paintings.

sign.post.town.description: A one sided town sign post, that you can plant into terrain.

sign.post.town.roof.description: A double sided town sign post, with roof, that you can plant into terrain.

sign.wooden.small.description: A 1-meter by 0.5-meter wooden sign that you can write on.

stash.small.description: A hidden, burried stash to keep your items safe. After placing, return to the stash and aim at the ground where you hid it and it will reveal itself.

sofa.description: A comfortable old sofa. A decorative item which provides comfort and seats two.

sofa.pattern.name: Sofa - Pattern
sofa.pattern.description: A comfortable old sofa with a floral pattern. A decorative item which provides comfort and seats two.

fishtrap.small.name: Survival Fish Trap
fishtrap.small.description: Traps fish, place on the shore and load with bait. The more bait loaded the bigger the chance of catching Trout.

table.description: Every home needs a table. A decorative item which provides comfort when in close proximity.

workbench1.description: This allows you to craft and unlock items requiring workbench level 1

workbench3.description: This allows you to craft and unlock items requiring workbench level 3

cupboard.tool.name: Tool Cupboard
cupboard.tool.description: Placing and authorising with the cupboard will make it so only you can build in a 50 meter radius of it. If you want your friends to build, they'll need to auth too. You should protect this.

cupboard.tool.retro.name: Retro Tool Cupboard
cupboard.tool.retro.description: Transform your tool cupboard experience with this modified Hi-Fi cabinet. Complete with retro displays indicating vital base data as well as frosted glass doors allowing you to view its contents of tools and resources!

cupboard.tool.shockbyte.name: Shockbyte Tool Cupboard
cupboard.tool.shockbyte.description: Ensure 100% Tool Cupboard uptime with this Tool Cupboard skin.

vending.machine.name: Vending Machine
vending.machine.description:
Trade your goods with other players safely by creating sell and buy orders.  

If a raider gains access to the rear panel, they will have free reign over all of your goodies. Keep it safe.

water.catcher.small.name: Small Water Catcher
water.catcher.small.description: Collects drinkable water from the air via rain and dew. Can be connected to other entities to provide water, 20ml a second.

water.purifier.description: A Water Purifier. Place overtop of a campfire. Will provide clean, drinkable water from salty, or stagnant water.

gunrack.single.1.horizontal.description: Artfully display your weapon with a handcrafted wall-mounted single weapon rack.

gunrack_wide.horizontal.description: Artfully display your arsenal with a handcrafted wall-mounted weapon rack.

apple.spoiled.description: A rotten apple. Eating it currently provides a tiny boost to health, hunger, and thirst.

black.raspberries.description: Black Raspberries picked from berry bushes. Eating it provides a small boost to health, hunger, and thirst.

blueberries.description: Blueberries picked from berry bushes. Eating it provides a small boost to health, hunger, and thirst.

botabag.description: A canteen used to carry Water. Left click to drink, right click to fill from water sources, or to pour out.

bread.loaf.name: Bread Loaf
bread.loaf.description: A loaf of bread, eating it provides a boost to health, hunger and hydration. Feeding to a horse will provide a boost t o its digestion and dung production for a short time.

grub.name: Grub
grub.description: A pale, fleshy insect that can be used for bait. Could also be eaten in desperate situations.

worm.name: Worm
worm.description: A small, writhing worm that can be used for bait. Could also be eaten in desperate situations.

cactusflesh.name: Cactus Flesh
cactusflesh.description: Flesh of a Cactus, contains water.

can.beans.description: Beans found as loot. Eating it provides a small boost to health, hunger, and thirst.

can.tuna.description: Chunked tuna found as loot. Eating it provides a small boost to health, hunger, and thirst.

chocolate.description: Chocolate Bar found as loot. Eating it provides a small boost to health, hunger, and thirst.

fish.anchovy.description: A small bony fish commonly found in large schools.

fish.catfish.name: Catfish
fish.catfish.description: A large, whiskered fresh water based predator. Eats everything, so you never know what you'll find in it's stomach.

fish.herring.name: Herring
fish.herring.description: A small fish commonly found in a variety of water sources.

fish.minnows.name: Minnows
fish.minnows.description: A Small group of edible fish.

fish.sardine.description: A small oily fish, commonly found in large schools.

fish.troutsmall.name: Small Trout
fish.troutsmall.description: A Small Trout. Good for a few meals.

fish.yellowperch.name: Yellow Perch
fish.yellowperch.description: A Yellow Perch, commonly found in freshwater rivers.

granolabar.name: Granola Bar
granolabar.description: Granola Bar found as loot. Eating it provides a small boost to health, hunger.

nucleus.name: Beehive Nucleus

flameturret.description: Automated Flame turret. Requires Low Grade Fuel. Sprays flames when triggered.

ammo.rocket.sam.name: SAM Ammo
ammo.rocket.sam.description: Ammunition for a SAM Site. This missile contains a rudimentary guidance system to help it navigate through strong winds.

clone.sunflower.description: A clipping of a sunflower plant.

seed.sunflower.description: Sunflower seeds can be found when picking wild Sunflowers.

clone.wheat.name: Wheat Clone
clone.wheat.description: A Clipping of a Wheat Plant.

seed.wheat.name: Wheat Seed
seed.wheat.description: Wheat seeds, found when eating wheat or harvesting wild crops. Plant in the ground or a planter to grow more.  Seeds grown in good conditions will have higher yields and grow faster.

fat.animal.name: Animal Fat
fat.animal.description: Harvested from animals, combine with cloth to create a low quality fuel source.

bone.fragments.name: Bone Fragments
bone.fragments.description: Extracted from animal carcass.  Used as a raw material to make bone weapons and armour.

cctv.camera.name: CCTV Camera
cctv.camera.description: A CCTV Camera system can be used for realtime surveillance and security around your base when powered and paired with the Computer Station.

charcoal.name: Charcoal
charcoal.description: Byproduct from campfires and furnaces used for crafting gunpowder.

cloth.name: Cloth
cloth.description: Cloth from an animal or a Hemp Bush. Used in many clothing items, weapons, and more.

crude.oil.name: Crude Oil
crude.oil.description: Raw Oil out of the ground, must be refined in a refinery to be used.

can.beans.empty.name: Empty Can Of Beans
can.beans.empty.description: An empty Can of Beans. Can be smelted into Metal Fragments.

can.tuna.empty.name: Empty Tuna Can
can.tuna.empty.description: An empty Can of Tuna. Can be smelted into Metal Fragments.

explosives.name: Explosives
explosives.description: A component used for crafting C4 and Rockets.

fertilizer.name: Fertilizer
fertilizer.description: Helps plants grow by increasing ground condition. Produced in a composter.

gunpowder.name: Gun Powder
gunpowder.description: Made from Sulfur and Charcoal, a key ingredient of anything that goes bang!

honeycomb.name: Honeycomb
honeycomb.description: Building blocks of a hive, taken from a natural beehive. Can be cooked in a furnace to guarantee honey, or extracted for honey and a small chance of a nucleus.

hq.metal.ore.name: High Quality Metal Ore
hq.metal.ore.description: A rock containing High Quality Metal. Can be smelted in a furnace.

metal.refined.name: High Quality Metal
metal.refined.description: High quality metal suitable for armor and weapons construction.

leather.name: Leather
leather.description: Leather from an animal. Used in many clothing items and more.

lowgradefuel.name: Low Grade Fuel
lowgradefuel.description: Low Grade Fuel, used to power light sources.

metal.fragments.name: Metal Fragments
metal.fragments.description: Metal Fragments. Smelted from Metal Ore, used in lots of different crafting recipes.

metal.ore.name: Metal Ore
metal.ore.description: A naturally occurring rock containing metal and metal compounds. You can extract this metal using a furnace.

paper.name: Paper
paper.description: Paper, a ingredient for Building plan and Note.

plantfiber.name: Plant Fiber
plantfiber.description: Fiber from dead plants. Can be composted.

water.radioactive.name: Radioactive Water
water.radioactive.description: Glowing water. Consuming will damage your health and irradiate you.

researchpaper.name: Research Paper
researchpaper.description: Use this item in a Research Bench to create blueprints of items.

water.salt.name: Salt Water
water.salt.description: Water with a high salt content. Consuming will damage your health.

scrap.name: Scrap
scrap.description: Scrap can be used in a Research table and Workbench to unlock and research items. Often used as a currency throughout the world.

stones.name: Stones
stones.description: Harvested from rocks using tools, basic building material.

sulfur.ore.name: Sulfur Ore
sulfur.ore.description: A rock containing sulfur. The sulfur can be extracted using a furnace.

sulfur.name: Sulfur
sulfur.description: Sulfur is commonly used in gunpowder, medicine, and matches. Matches release sulfur dioxide when they burn, giving them their smell. Sulfur is an essential component to living cells. Many proteins contain sulfur. It is also used as a pesticide on organic farms.

targeting.computer.name: Targeting Computer
targeting.computer.description: A computer loaded with software that can analyze a video and produce rotational deltas to individual objects contained in the feed.

water.name: Water
water.description: Water. Drinking it will alleviate your thirst.

wood.name: Wood
wood.description: Wood. Collected from trees and used in many crafting recipes. It's also needed to cook in camp-fires.

coolingtea.name: Cooling Tea
coolingtea.description: A cooling tea that temporarily decreases your max and core temperature.

craftingtea_quality.name: Crafting Quality Tea
craftingtea_quality.description: A tea that increases the chances of a higher quality crafting outcome.

harvestingtea.name: Harvesting Tea
harvestingtea.description: A basic tea that temporarily increases the amount of resources you receive from harvesting corpses a small amount.

healingtea.advanced.name: Advanced Healing Tea
healingtea.advanced.description: An advanced healing tea, provides hydration and heals you a moderate amount over time.

healingtea.name: Basic Healing Tea
healingtea.description: A basic healing tea, provides hydration and heals you a small amount over time.

healingtea.pure.name: Pure Healing Tea
healingtea.pure.description: A pure healing tea, provides hydration and heals you a large amount over time.

maxhealthtea.advanced.name: Advanced Max Health Tea
maxhealthtea.advanced.description: An advanced health tea, provides hydration and temporarily boosts maximum health a moderate amount.

maxhealthtea.name: Basic Max Health Tea
maxhealthtea.description: A basic health tea, provides hydration and temporarily boosts maximum health a small amount.

maxhealthtea.pure.name: Pure Max Health Tea
maxhealthtea.pure.description: An advanced health tea, provides hydration and temporarily boosts maximum health a large amount.

oretea.advanced.name: Advanced Ore Tea
oretea.advanced.description: An advanced ore tea, provides hydration and temporarily increases your yield from ores a moderate amount.

oretea.name: Basic Ore Tea
oretea.description: A basic ore tea, provides hydration and temporarily increases your yield from harvesting ores a small amount.

oretea.pure.name: Pure Ore Tea
oretea.pure.description: A pure ore tea, provides hydration and temporarily increases your yield when harvesting ores a large amount.

radiationremovetea.advanced.name: Advanced Rad. Removal Tea
radiationremovetea.advanced.description: A tea that removes some radiation.

radiationremovetea.name: Rad. Removal Tea
radiationremovetea.description: A tea that removes some radiation.

radiationremovetea.pure.name: Pure Rad. Removal Tea
radiationremovetea.pure.description: A tea that removes some radiation.

radiationresisttea.advanced.name: Advanced Anti-Rad Tea
radiationresisttea.advanced.description: An advanced tea that provides some hydration and temporarily increases your resistance to radiation a moderate amount.

radiationresisttea.name: Basic Anti-Rad Tea
radiationresisttea.description: A basic tea that provides hydration and temporarily increases your resistance to radiation a small amount.

radiationresisttea.pure.name: Pure Anti-Rad Tea
radiationresisttea.pure.description: A pure tea that provides hydration and temporarily increases your resistance to radiation a large amount.

scraptea.advanced.description: An advanced scrap tea, temporarily increases the amount of scrap you recieve from barrels a moderate amount.

scraptea.description: A basic scrap tea, temporarily increases the amount of scrap you recieve from barrels a small amount.

scraptea.pure.name: Pure Scrap Tea
scraptea.pure.description: A pure scrap tea, temporarily increases the amount of scrap you recieve from barrels a large amount.

supertea.name: Super Serum
supertea.description: Super Serum,  more ore, more wood, more scrap

warmingtea.name: Warming Tea
warmingtea.description: A warming tea that temporarily increases both your core and minimum temperature.

woodtea.advanced.name: Advanced Wood Tea
woodtea.advanced.description: An advanced wood tea, temporarily increases the yield from cutting trees a moderate amount.

woodtea.name: Basic Wood Tea
woodtea.description: A basic wood tea, temporarily increases the yield from cutting trees a small amount.

woodtea.pure.name: Pure Wood Tea
woodtea.pure.description: A pure wood tea, temporarily increases the yield from cutting trees a large amount.

antiradpills.name: Anti-Radiation Pills
antiradpills.description: Taking these pills will lower your radiation level. WARNING: May cause extreme dehydration.

tool.binoculars.name: Binoculars
tool.binoculars.description: Binoculars allowing you to see objects at great length.

explosive.timed.name: Timed Explosive Charge
explosive.timed.description: C4, useful for breaking into bases.

tool.camera.name: Camera
tool.camera.description: A camera. Take screenshots with primary fire, zoom in and out with secondary fire, and lock focus with third fire.

rf.detonator.name: RF Transmitter
rf.detonator.description: A hand held RF signal broadcaster. Left click to broadcast. Configurable with right mouse.

fishingrod.handmade.name: Handmade Fishing Rod
fishingrod.handmade.description: Use [attack2] to cast out the line and wait for a bite. Requires bait.

flare.name: Flare
flare.description: Light up the night sky with this brand new red flare!

flashlight.held.name: Flashlight
flashlight.held.description: A powerful flashlight which illuminates your surroundings and can be used as a weapon.

geiger.counter.name: Geiger Counter
geiger.counter.description: A geiger counter used by scientists

hosetool.name: Hose Tool
hosetool.description: A tool used to make fluid connections between objects. Aim at an object and click on an input/output handle, then click on another object's input/output handle to form a connection.

jackhammer.name: Jackhammer
jackhammer.description: A Pneumatic Jackhammer to blast through ore nodes. The sheer power of this device requires no aiming as all weak spots will be instantly destroyed. Works well on human flesh. Can be refilled at a Workbench.

keycard_blue.name: Blue Keycard
keycard_blue.description: A keycard with medium level clearance.

keycard_green.name: Green Keycard
keycard_green.description: A low level clearance card granting access to basic areas.

keycard_red.name: Red Keycard
keycard_red.description: A keycard with advanced clearance, grants access to top level areas

largemedkit.name: Large Medkit
largemedkit.description:
A large medkit that heals you to max health over time and stops any bleeding instantly.

Guarantees 100% recovery from the wounded state if placed in your toolbar.

concretehatchet.name: Concrete Hatchet
concretehatchet.description: A salvaged piece of concrete and rebar which can be used to harvest wood

concretepickaxe.name: Concrete Pickaxe
concretepickaxe.description: A salvaged piece of concrete and rebar with a sharp edge. Can be used to harvest Stone, Metal ore and Sulfur ore.

lumberjack.hatchet.name: Prototype Hatchet
lumberjack.hatchet.description: A prototype field hatchet, useful for gathering wood

lumberjack.pickaxe.name: Prototype Pickaxe
lumberjack.pickaxe.description: A prototype field pickaxe. Useful for gathering ore from rocks.

map.name: Paper Map
map.description:
Helps you figure out where you are. You can annotate the map by right-clicking and drawing on it.


Drag the map into your belt bar to make it active. You will then be able to view the map by holding down the map button (G by default).

syringe.medical.name: Medical Syringe
syringe.medical.description: Heal yourself or others with this syringe. Left-click heals you, right-click heals a target.

metal.detector.name: Metal Detector
metal.detector.description: Detects metal objects which may otherwise be hidden. When the light flashes, or you hear a beep, aim to search for items. Increase the bar until a flag appears. Dig at the flag with a melee item to reveal what it is. Different areas yield different rewards

rf_pager.name: RF Pager
rf_pager.description: An RF Pager. An audible tone will be produced when a signal is picked up on the listening frequency. Can be set to silent mode.

pipetool.name: Pipe Tool
pipetool.description: A tool used to make connections between industrial objects. Aim at an object and click on an input/output handle, then click on another object's input/output handle to form a connection. Holding right mouse will clear or cancel a connection.

building.planner.name: Building Plan
building.planner.description: A building plan. You can use this to craft buildings - right click when equipped for more options.

shovel.name: Shovel
shovel.description: A shovel for digging up stuff

grenade.smoke.name: Smoke Grenade
grenade.smoke.description: Produces a large cloud of opaque greyish white smoke.

spraycan.name: Spray Can
spraycan.description: Use the Spray Can to leave Tags or reskin your items. Press [attack] to spray and [attack2] to reskin items.

supply.signal.name: Supply Signal
supply.signal.description: Purple signal smoke. Use to mark a location for an airdrop.

surveycharge.name: Survey Charge
surveycharge.description: Use this on the terrain to see which resources are available for mining.

walkietalkie.name: Walkie Talkie
walkietalkie.description: A walkie talkie set to an unknown channel

wiretool.name: Wire Tool
wiretool.description: A tool used to make connections between electrical objects. Aim at an object and click on an input/output handle, then click on another object's input/output handle to form a connection. Holding right mouse will clear or cancel a connection.

vehicle.1mod.cockpit.name: Cockpit Vehicle Module
vehicle.1mod.cockpit.description: Single module cockpit for a driver and one passenger.

vehicle.1mod.cockpit.armored.name: Armored Cockpit Vehicle Module
vehicle.1mod.cockpit.armored.description: Single module armored cockpit for a driver and one passenger.

vehicle.1mod.cockpit.with.engine.name: Cockpit With Engine Vehicle Module
vehicle.1mod.cockpit.with.engine.description: Single module cockpit for a driver and one passenger, with a small engine.

vehicle.1mod.passengers.armored.name: Armored Passenger Vehicle Module
vehicle.1mod.passengers.armored.description: Single module armored seating for two passengers.

vehicle.1mod.rear.seats.name: Rear Seats Vehicle Module
vehicle.1mod.rear.seats.description: Single module seating for two passengers.

vehicle.1mod.taxi.name: Taxi Vehicle Module
vehicle.1mod.taxi.description: Single module seating for two passengers, with protection at the front.

vehicle.2mod.camper.name: Camper Vehicle Module
vehicle.2mod.camper.description: Dual module camper that allows up to 4 players to respawn. Also includes a barbecue, a locker and a small box for item storage.

vehicle.car_radio.name: Car Radio
vehicle.car_radio.description: A small radio to use in cars. Will only work while the car is turned on.

boombox.name: Boom Box
boombox.description: A large speaker to play recorded cassette tapes which can also stream audio from the internet. Open the settings to change audio options.

fun.boomboxportable.name: Portable Boom Box
fun.boomboxportable.description: A portable Boom Box that can play tapes and internet audio streams. [attack] to start/stop and [attack2] to modify settings.

cassette.name: Cassette - Long
cassette.description: A tape that you can record audio on to using a Cassette Recorder. Stores up to 30s of audio.

cassette.medium.name: Cassette - Medium
cassette.medium.description: A tape that you can record audio on to using a Cassette Recorder. Stores up to 20s of audio.

cassette.short.name: Cassette - Short
cassette.short.description: A tape that you can record audio on to using a Cassette Recorder. Stores up to 10s of audio.

fun.casetterecorder.name: Cassette Recorder
fun.casetterecorder.description: Insert a cassette and play the recorded audio with [attack], [attack2] to record new audio and [+reload] to throw.

discoball.name: Disco Ball
discoball.description: Get groovy with this stunning disco ball.

discofloor.name: Disco Floor
discofloor.description: A vibrant flashing floor that pulses in time to music.

discofloor.largetiles.name: Disco Floor
discofloor.largetiles.description: A vibrant flashing floor that pulses in time to music.

connected.speaker.name: Connected Speaker
connected.speaker.description: A small speaker that will play any audio from a connected Boom Box.

laserlight.name: Laser Light
laserlight.description: A small device that shoots out visible lasers in time to music.

megaphone.name: Megaphone
megaphone.description: A megaphone that lets you broadcast your voice. [attack] to activate your voice.

microphonestand.name: Microphone Stand
microphonestand.description: A powered microphone that lets you broadcast your voice. Press [+attack2] to change voice mode between high and low pitch.

mobilephone.name: Mobile Phone
mobilephone.description: A mobile phone that lets you place calls from anywhere. Truly cutting edge Cobalt technology. Use [attack] to access the dialer.

soundlight.name: Sound Light
soundlight.description: A light that will pulse in time to music when connected to a Boom Box.

telephone.name: Telephone
telephone.description: Use the telephone to call other telephones on the island!

wallpaper.name: Wallpaper
wallpaper.description: Transform your base from a rusty shack to a cozy hideout with this sleek wallpaper. A nice touch of style - until the next raid, at least.

weapon.mod.8x.scope.name: Variable Zoom Scope
weapon.mod.8x.scope.description: A large military-grade scope that can be configured from 4x zoom to 16x zoom.

weapon.mod.burstmodule.name: Burst Module
weapon.mod.burstmodule.description: Forces the weapon to fire in 3 round bursts.

weapon.mod.flashlight.name: Weapon flashlight
weapon.mod.flashlight.description: Attaches to a weapon. Provides user with a beam of light. Pressing F (default) to toggle light.

weapon.mod.gascompressionovedrive.name: Gas Compression Overdrive
weapon.mod.gascompressionovedrive.description: An internal weapon mod which compresses and directs gasses used for cycling the weapon to the barrel, effectively increasing projectile velocity and damage at the expense of cycle rate.

weapon.mod.holosight.name: Holosight
weapon.mod.holosight.description: Uses laser projection to create a holographic sight which is always pointing at the target regardless of view angle.

weapon.mod.lasersight.name: Weapon Lasersight
weapon.mod.lasersight.description: Attaches to a weapon. Provides user with a guiding laser and reduces weapon sway.

weapon.mod.muzzleboost.name: Muzzle Boost
weapon.mod.muzzleboost.description: Increases weapon fire rate by channeling gasses back into the weapon cycling it faster, at the cost of bullet accuracy.

weapon.mod.muzzlebrake.name: Muzzle Brake
weapon.mod.muzzlebrake.description: Lowers recoil felt by the operator but can make bullet path more unpredictable and dealing slightly less damage to your foes.

weapon.mod.simplesight.name: Simple Handmade Sight
weapon.mod.simplesight.description: A poorly made sight, slightly better than iron sights.

weapon.mod.silencer.name: Silencer
weapon.mod.silencer.description: Significantly reduces the sound of gunfire, and completely removes any visible muzzle flash.

rifle.ak.diver.name: Abyss Assault Rifle
rifle.ak.diver.description: A waterlogged assault rifle from the abyss

rifle.ak.med.name: Medieval Assault Rifle
rifle.ak.med.description: Medieval themed high damage machine rifle.

bandage.name: Bandage
bandage.description: Heal yourself or others with this bandage. Left-click heals you, right-click heals a target.

grenade.bee.name: Bee Grenade
grenade.bee.description: A fragile glass jar, throw it to unleash a swarm of bees on the nearest target. The bees will deal damage quickly but they don't like fire or water.

blunderbuss.name: Blunderbuss
blunderbuss.description: A Shotgun with two barrels allowing two shots to be fired in quick succession before needing to reload.

rifle.bolt.name: Bolt Action Rifle
rifle.bolt.description: A High powered, highly accurate, long range rifle.

bone.club.name: Bone Club
bone.club.description: A blunt weapon made from a femur. All around basic gathering tool.

knife.bone.name: Bone Knife
knife.bone.description: Melee weapon crafted from bone fragments. Good for harvesting carcases.

bow.hunting.name: Hunting Bow
bow.hunting.description: Hunting Bow, useful for short to medium range combat and hunting.

cakefiveyear.name: Birthday Cake
cakefiveyear.description: A very special and happy birthday to Rust!

chainsaw.name: Chainsaw
chainsaw.description: A Chainsaw. Very effective at cutting trees in addition to soft fleshy objects. Requires Low Grade Fuel to run.

salvaged.cleaver.name: Salvaged Cleaver
salvaged.cleaver.description: A powerful 2-handed melee weapon with high damage.

spear.cny.name: Lunar New Year Spear
spear.cny.description: A Chinese themed New Year themed metal Spear

bow.compound.name: Compound Bow
bow.compound.description: A very powerful bow. Can only be fully drawn while stationary. Keep still for bonus damage and speed.

diverhatchet.name: Abyss Metal Hatchet
diverhatchet.description: Metal hatchet, reclaimed from the abyss, perfect for survival and crafting

diverpickaxe.name: Abyss Metal Pickaxe
diverpickaxe.description: Plucked from the abyss, this Metal Pickaxe is a prized possession for any survivor

divertorch.name: Abyss Torch
divertorch.description: Illuminate the underwater depths with this durable and waterproof diving torch

shotgun.double.name: Double Barrel Shotgun
shotgun.double.description: A Shotgun with two barrels allowing two shots to be fired in quick succession before needing to reload.

pistol.eoka.name: Eoka Pistol
pistol.eoka.description: A very cheap, very ineffective, and very unreliable pistol that fires shells.

flamethrower.name: Flame Thrower
flamethrower.description: A Flamethrower. Uses low grade fuel as ammunition.

grenade.flashbang.name: Flashbang
grenade.flashbang.description: A bright explosive device which blinds and disorients anyone near it upon detonation

frontier_hatchet.name: Frontier Hatchet
frontier_hatchet.description: A Frontier Hatchet, useful for chopping trees and dismembering corpses.

multiplegrenadelauncher.name: Multiple Grenade Launcher
multiplegrenadelauncher.description: A 40MM six barrel, semi automatic grenade launcher

mace.baseballbat.name: Baseball Bat
mace.baseballbat.description: A baseball bat wrapped in barbed wire

knife.butcher.name: Butcher Knife
knife.butcher.description: A sharp butcher knife. Extremely good at harvesting flesh from both dead or alive bodies.

pitchfork.name: Pitchfork
pitchfork.description: A 3 pronged pitchfork. Extremely easy to hit targets with.

sickle.name: Sickle
sickle.description: A very sharp curved cutting weapon. While its traditional role was to cut grass, this tool is also extremely versatile at cutting throats, perhaps trees, too.

vampire.stake.name: Vampire Stake
vampire.stake.description: A stake adorned with special properties making it able to release the soul of undead creatures with a single strike, as well as yield extra loot from their remains.

hammer.name: Hammer
hammer.description: A Hammer, used to upgrade building materials. Right-click for the options. You can also pick up deployed objects while the hammer is equipped.

hatchet.name: Hatchet
hatchet.description: A Hatchet, useful for chopping trees and dismembering corpses.

hmlmg.name: HMLMG
